    <div class="information__container">
        <div class="information__content">
            <p class="information__text">
                Our programme is structured to help you achieve your life goals. We make sure our students stand out academically and possess essential corporate traits that make them stand out among their peers. Our payment plans are super convenient for anyone who wants the best quality for their money. 
            </p>
        </div>
